            <p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="1">I was testing /face last night and it seems to have a dam short range .. a lot shorter than the range of a normal DD, never mind the extra distance a Bow can pull.<br>
<br>
Arrow sticking out of the body ... ok this is a little over the top.. if reality had any hand in the game .. if an arrow 'actually' sticks in you .. i can say with hand on heart you aint gonna be in the same possition 5 sec latter.<br>
<br>
Arrow flying .. urmmm well .. we can see bolts already so seeing the arrow is not that much different .. i hope it is less obvious.<br>
<br>
As i have put forward on other threads IMO<br>
.. Scouts are Archers and trackers (dont get onto EQ) and not some old world Long range Assissins..</font></p>
             
