            <p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="1">I couldn't care less about being an assasin.  I just want to be a "scout".<br>
<br>
Let's see, I can't remain stealthed and have anything close to a normal walk speed much less a normal run speed.  <br>
<br>
I am reduced to wearing only studded armor, but only run as fast unstealthed as an armsman in full plate.  <br>
<br>
I have no track.  <br>
<br>
I have no speed enhancements whatsoever.  <br>
<br>
I have NO safe fall ability to compensate for my knowledge of the terrain I am scouting.<br>
<br>
How exactly am I supposed to scout anything?<br>
<br>
So, yeah, we've been reduced to assasins at range.  Not our fault.  Some of us REALLY want to be scouts.</font></p>
             
