            <p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="1"><blockquote><font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1">quote:</font><hr><br>
Let's see, I can't remain stealthy and have anything close to a normal walk speed much less a normal run speed.<br>
