<br>
<blockquote><font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1">quote:</font><hr><br>
I am reduced to wearing only studded armour, but only run as fast unstealthed as an armsman in full plate. <br>
<hr></blockquote><br>
<br>
agree, <br>
<br>
but does that mean casters should run faster ? .. I dont think so, they do not have the strength or endurance .. this is what the encumbrance system is all about.<br>
<br>
<blockquote><font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1">quote:</font><hr><br>
